<Document>
  <name>San Saba County — Unmapped Historical Markers</name>
  <description>THC markers in San Saba County without an HMDB id (isMissing excluded). 9 with THC coords; 0 geocoded from address; 10 omitted (no usable address).</description>
  <Placemark>
    <name>Adams Cemetery</name>
